Body:
Description: I'm looking for a setting to remove old computers that are no longer reporting in from the console. I have tried manually deleting them from Device Control > Computers, but they just re-appear.

Additionally, I've noticed what appears to be a bug -- at one point I saw that we had 300+ computers in the server, but the CSV export from Device Control > List of Computers - with "show all entries" marked - the CSV only exports 200 devices.

Tried reproducing.

From 364 computers. Deleted till 149 remained

64 offline and unlicensed

Waiting for customer to check if the computers come back.
